<mxfile host="app.diagrams.net">
  <diagram name="第 1 页" id="qsyoMNZuB0qPF_6azBv1">
    <mxGraphModel dx="2636" dy="1722" grid="0" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="0" pageScale="1" pageWidth="827" pageHeight="1169" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0" />
        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <UserObject label="" mermaidData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;sequenceDiagram\n    autonumber\n    participant N as NUnit 运行器\n    participant T as 测试类 PcReportOpenApiV2Tests&lt;br/&gt;(FixtureRequired + Slow)\n    participant F as RunShopFixture\n    participant FC as ApiFixtureContext&lt;br/&gt;(RestClient / OpenApiV2Client / Cleanup栈)\n    participant SG as FixtureSafetyGuard\n    participant API as T+ 目标系统&lt;br/&gt;(REST · OpenAPI v2 · SQL)\n\n    Note over T: ① [OneTimeSetUp] 启动\n    N-&gt;&gt;T: 触发测试类\n    T-&gt;&gt;F: EnsureAsync(ReportData)\n\n    Note over F,FC: ② 创建上下文 + 三层安全闸\n    F-&gt;&gt;FC: CreateFixtureContextOrIgnore()\n    FC-&gt;&gt;FC: Load() 加载本地 json 配置\n    F-&gt;&gt;SG: RequireFixtureWriteEnabled&lt;br/&gt;(EnableFixtureWrite=true?)\n    F-&gt;&gt;SG: RequireMarketingOrgIds&lt;br/&gt;(Current/Other 组织 ID?)\n    F-&gt;&gt;SG: AssertConfiguredPrefixAllowsRunShopCodes&lt;br/&gt;(编码前缀=APITEST_?)\n    Note right of SG: 任一不满足 → Assert.Ignore&lt;br/&gt;测试跳过,不报错\n\n    Note over F: ③ 认证\n    F-&gt;&gt;API: RestClient.AuthenticateAsync()&lt;br/&gt;获取 T+ Token\n\n    Note over F,API: ④ 按位掩码条件化准备数据\n    loop 逐个判定 RequiresXxx(dependencies)\n        F-&gt;&gt;F: 该依赖位是否命中?\n        alt 命中(如 CurrentOrgCustomer)\n            F-&gt;&gt;API: 调用创建 API&lt;br/&gt;(客户/存货/路线/拜访计划/记录)\n            API--&gt;&gt;F: 返回业务对象 ID\n            F-&gt;&gt;FC: Cleanup栈.Add(描述, 清理回调)\n            Note right of FC: 逆序清理注册\n        else 未命中(如 OtherOrgRoute)\n            Note right of F: 跳过,不准备该数据\n        end\n    end\n    Note over F: 准备顺序(有依赖关系):&lt;br/&gt;拜访人员→双组织客户→清理阻塞→存货→报表源→&lt;br/&gt;当前路线→其他路线→当前拜访计划→其他拜访计划→&lt;br/&gt;当前拜访记录→其他拜访记录\n\n    F--&gt;&gt;T: 返回完整装配的 Fixture&lt;br/&gt;(含双组织数据 + 客户端)\n\n    Note over T,API: ⑤ 测试方法执行(可多个)\n    T-&gt;&gt;F: fixture.OpenApiV2Client.CallFormAsync(&lt;br/&gt;reportQuery / GetReportData)\n    F-&gt;&gt;API: HTTP POST OpenAPI v2\n    API--&gt;&gt;F: 报表 JSON (Rows / TaskSessionID)\n    F--&gt;&gt;T: 响应封装\n    T-&gt;&gt;T: AssertOpenApiReportSuccess&lt;br/&gt;+ 已知缺陷容错判定&lt;br/&gt;(SQL4104 / 临时表失败 → Pass)\n\n    Note over T: ⑥ [OneTimeTearDown] 自动清理\n    T-&gt;&gt;F: fixture.DisposeAsync()\n    F-&gt;&gt;FC: Cleanup.RunAllAsync()\n    Note right of FC: LIFO 逆序执行: 拜访记录→拜访计划→...→客户\n    FC-&gt;&gt;API: 逐项删除测试数据\n    F--&gt;&gt;N: 测试完成,数据已还原&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;config&quot;: null&#xa;}" id="78">
          <mxCell connectable="0" parent="1" style="group;transparentBounds=1;editIcon=1;lockedGroup=0;groupPadding=20;" vertex="1">
